    Class Description
    FlashLight
    The FlashLight Class is used to show Trump's flashlight beam that can "kill" immigrants.
    GameDriver
    The GameDriver Class runs the game
    GamePanel
    The Gameboard controls most of the main program It has both players and creates guards.
    GamePanel.Closer  
    GamePanel.Key
    Key Listener controls movement and limit of immigrants and trump.
    Guard
    Guards are objects that move up and down in the game screen, They have starting x and y positions and have ImageIcons that are painted in the GamePanel
    Immigrants
    The Immigrants class is the class of the player in the game.
    ImmWin
    ImmWin (Immigrant Win) is a panel that is run when the immigrant wins the game.
    StartPanel
    The StartPanel is the panel that is shown when the driver is run.
    StartPanel.Back  
    StartPanel.Credits  
    StartPanel.Instructions  
    StartPanel.Stats  
    Trump
    The Trump class is the class that controls the sprite trump in the GamePanel, it contains its x and y positions
    TrumpWin
    TrumpWin is a panel that is run when the immigrant wins the game.
